      "raw_text": "A new tariff list containing rates\nfrom Portland, Tacoma, Seattle and\nSnohomsh, has been announced by the\nNorthern Pacific to and from points on\nthe Washington Central line. The list\nincludes So articles. The greatest re-\nduction is on cotton goods, which have\nbeen given rate of 81, which is 4S\ncents less than heretofore But this\nsection handles no cotton goods in\ncarload lots. The rate in this partic-\nular was made more to equalize the\n81 rate to Spokane more than anything\nelse, which will be effective April 10."
